{"tid":1068454,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【黃背心運動】部署5,000警力示威仍失控 巴黎警隊一哥被炒","createTime":"2019-03-19T08:58:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-19T14:22:53.000Z","uid":47359,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"99be4ae72db18d709939dad634ad818c4e5050e6","tid":1068454,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T08:58:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190319&amp;s=10793140&amp;a=59384402\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190319%26s%3D10793140%26a%3D59384402&d=pHv7ulxaPAPTUdGhwq1YMQzuSh5pVPBxDrYQpIU1Wbo%3D&h=ba0f2296\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190319%26s%3D10793140%26a%3D59384402&h=d81a22a2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190319&amp;s=10793140&amp;a=59384402</a><br />\n<br />\n法國反政府「黃背心運動」上周末一輪又再失控，總理菲利普（Edouard Philippe）周一宣佈炒掉巴黎市警察局長德爾皮埃什（Michel Delpuech）。<br />\n<br />\n「黃背心」抗議運動四個月來每周末都在法國上演的，上周六第18輪示威再演變成暴力衝突。縱然巴黎警方部署了5,000警力，人數遠超幾百名「暴徒」，但依然失控，有示威者在香榭麗舍大道大肆破壞，縱火燒餐廳、銀行和搶掠名店，造成約60人受傷，一對母子幾乎葬身火海。<br />\n<br />\n廣告<br />\n<br />\n總統馬克龍縮短滑雪假期，與政府部長開會，要求菲利普適當回應亂局。菲利普坦承政府在維護公共治安上失職，而德爾皮埃什成為「黃背心運動」4個多月來第一位下台高官。<br />\n<br />\n菲利普表示會將參加非法集會的罰款金額從38歐元（338港元）提高至135歐元（1,201港元），還表示一旦發現香榭麗舍大道或其他地方的集會有滋事分子，會立即禁止示威。<br />\n<br />\n路透社／英國廣播公司"},{"pid":"5a550f0d43cd9a005cabe2497d04623b784c1097","tid":1068454,"uid":111253,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T09:01:12.000Z","msg":"馬文龍 自己搞鑊粥要總理硬食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"593f253f6f2d0a844886b713f6fd80bf10d0efd6","tid":1068454,"uid":111253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T09:01:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>馬交龍 自己搞鑊粥要總理硬食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"28ca3bd272b061599055743f1cbd019d23452774","tid":1068454,"uid":99929,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T09:02:34.000Z","msg":"Hi關sir<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1284d5272da558ac3ffa060ac5f9d278d64f423e","tid":1068454,"uid":169154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5a550f0d43cd9a005cabe2497d04623b784c1097","tid":1068454,"uid":111253,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T09:01:12.000Z","msg":"馬文龍 自己搞鑊粥要總理硬食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T09:06:31.000Z","msg":"縮短滑雪假期<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d6e1b33d3bd1efa5087f3f2542055d335cf8978","tid":1068454,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T09:07:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/2RaF_wGi9mQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F2RaF_wGi9mQ&d=pHv7ulxaPAPTUdGhwq1YMQzuSh5pVPBxDrYQpIU1Wbo%3D&h=6e0bc684\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/2RaF_wGi9mQ</a>"},{"pid":"3ff59e3ca6a3be7ba877140ee743cee0bd310dd3","tid":1068454,"uid":175623,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T09:09:30.000Z","msg":"人地警方做得幾好"},{"pid":"a5bb37f8b7dd0922a2106c053d2e779d81fd2a69","tid":1068454,"uid":79563,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T09:12:02.000Z","msg":"華文傳媒：<br />\n<br />\n法國打到九彩名店被搶被燒叫「示威」 / 「運動」<br />\n<br />\n香港掟兩粒磚叫「暴動」"},{"pid":"5bc5479cf70f091a17ed93627b3dda9d6b8129f7","tid":1068454,"uid":47359,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T09:12:12.000Z","msg":"參加非法集會的罰款金額從38歐元（338港元）提高至135歐元（1,201港元）<br />\n<br />\n香港非法集會：坐監"},{"pid":"e3845c44fd68f9a3ebaf06dde8ad2c77a5d3a350","tid":1068454,"uid":38523,"like":2,"dislike"